{
  "stem": "5551.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But soon thereafter, I was told that we can no longer be in one another's home, or be seen together, because these are the new directives that rule the party.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And soon there was a takeover of Germany by the Nazi party by bringing Hitler to power.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "From then on it went downhill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And things got to be more and more dangerous.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But in 1932, when I was a child, I remember well the weekends when the communists, mainly the communists, were fighting the Nazis in the streets of Breslau.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This was a frequent occurrence, and amongst the communists at that time, there was a significant constituents of Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because this was the only truly organized opposition to Hitler at that time, 1932.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "All of it vanished after 1933 because communist activists and opposition leaders and members were eliminated, whether they were Jewish, German, or any other way.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents were progressive people, but traditionally Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not exceedingly religious, but we carried on with Jewish tradition in the sense of Sabbath celebration, a Seder, or holidays.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a sort of kosher in our-- in our house, but not-- it was not enough to make my grandfather comfortable eating in our house.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Older.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not much older, just 18 months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very well.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a gifted one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a straight-A student, and generally liked and-- and considered promising.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the black sheep, actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I had the wildest ideas as a child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I was punished a lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
